data.title: Deans' List for fall 2023
data.meta_description: SUNY Oswego recognizes its high academic achievers with its Deans' List for fall 2023. Deans' List students are those attaining semester grade-point averages between 3.3 and 3.79 while carrying required academic credits.
data.text:
SUNY Oswego recognizes its high academic achievers with its Deans' List for fall 2023. Deans' List students are those attaining semester grade-point averages between 3.3 and 3.79 while carrying required academic credits. Our congratulations to them all! (Also check out our President's List.)
